===Noun===
{{en-noun|polyhedra|pl2=polyhedrons}}

# {{context|geometry|lang=en}} A [[solid]] [[figure]] with many flat [[face]]s and straight edges.
# {{context|optics|lang=en}} A [[polyscope]], or multiplying glass.

